@103740 = ~This unusual trident-shaped spear is crafted by Neverwinter's finest blacksmiths. How they managed to make this masterpiece from a simple weakly enchanted spear remains a mystery, it is only known that it required Fairy Dust. The trident is simply filled with Fairy Magic, it is able to blind enemies, make its owner invisible and beat enemies with electricity. In addition, the wielder becomes more agile when wielding this weapon.

