@2000210 = ~Neverwinter Nights~
@2000200 = ~~

@2000300 = ~The Great Plague from the North... You have heard vague rumours of it, slipping past like the shadows of scurrying rats in the dark alleys of Athkatla. In the docks, the sailors discussed the deadly plague that was ruthlessly decimating the population of Neverwinter. Several of their ships turned back home, away from Neverwinter, under the threat of sinking. The infestation raging through that North city was whispered in the tavern by a few traders who were fortunate enough to survive. Lady Aribeth, the paladin of Tyr, called out for an heroes to save Neverwinter, as told by the few adventurers who planned to try their luck there. 

So you have finally decided to travel there. Whatever motivated you to save the Jewel of the North from the plague - a desire for new adventures, a desire to glorify your name or, perhaps, the generous reward promised to the saviours of the city - you knew one thing for sure: difficult trials awaited you in the harsh lands that do not forgive weakness. Having gathered the gold you needed to travel, you set off on the long journey to the North.~
